Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:14.16,梢,,0,0,0,,对 去了「PLAZA」逛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.06,0:15:12.83,缀,,0,0,0,,PLAZA
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.49,0:15:14.16,缀,,0,0,0,,PLAZA
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.16,0:15:14.73,乃,,0,0,0,,PLAZA
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:15.86,帆,,0,0,0,,是呢
